Classes and interfaces related to routine builders.

    ConfigurableBuilder
    Interface defining a configurable builder.

    Interface defining a builder of routine objects.

    Class storing the routine configuration.

  • Exception Summary

    Exception indicating that no room in the output channel buffer became available before the specific timeout elapsed.
